{
  "title": "Enduse risks",
  "description": "**You can explore here:**\n\n Financial risk factor variables, called “risk factor pathways”. The methodology is explained in the UNEP-FI publication [“Extending Our Horizons”](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41560-018-0179-z). \n\n  Here, we focus on risk factor pathways for the end use sector in mitigation scenarios. They help to understand the transformations in the end use sector under a climate target, how energy demand, costs, required and investments change.\n ",
